# 1. Model Choice: Used DecisionTreeClassifier with max_depth=5. It is significantly more energy-efficient than XGBoost 
#    or Deep Learning, requiring minimal CPU cycles for inference and training while maintaining high accuracy for tabular NIDS data.
# 2. Preprocessing: Implemented a scikit-learn Pipeline to prevent data leakage and ensure reproducibility. 
